    {
      "role": "user",
      "content": "That's a good start. Can you expand on that a bit more for the students? I want to make sure they really understand why this doctrine is so essential for protecting people's rights from being taken away by unfair laws. Could you write a paragraph that emphasizes why we need substantive due process to ensure justice for marginalized groups?",
